DESCRIPTION="
free and open-source Touhou Project fangame (vendored)

Taisei Project is an open source fan-game set in the world
of Tōhō Project. It is a top-down vertical-scrolling curtain
fire shooting game (STG), also known as a \"bullet hell\" or
\"danmaku.\"
"

